{
  "video_id": "vNDhu2uqfdo",
  "title": "Mary Lou Jepsen: Could future devices read images from our brains?",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12607.0,
      "end_time": 15114.0,
      "text": "I had brain surgery 18 years ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15115.0,
      "end_time": 17682.0,
      "text": "and since that time, brain science has become"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 17682.0,
      "end_time": 19680.0,
      "text": "a personal passion of mine."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 19681.0,
      "end_time": 21916.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m actually an engineer."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 21916.0,
      "end_time": 24432.0,
      "text": "And first let me say, I recently joined"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 24432.0,
      "end_time": 25980.0,
      "text": "Google&#39;s Moonshot group,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 25981.0,
      "end_time": 27193.0,
      "text": "where I had a division,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 27193.0,
      "end_time": 29374.0,
      "text": "the display division in Google X,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 29374.0,
      "end_time": 31996.0,
      "text": "and the brain science work I&#39;m speaking about today"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 31996.0,
      "end_time": 34917.0,
      "text": "is work I did before I joined Google"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 34917.0,
      "end_time": 37249.0,
      "text": "and on the side outside of Google."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 37249.0,
      "end_time": 40432.0,
      "text": "So that said, there&#39;s a stigma"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 40432.0,
      "end_time": 42717.0,
      "text": "when you have brain surgery."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 42717.0,
      "end_time": 45540.0,
      "text": "Are you still smart or not?"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 45540.0,
      "end_time": 49388.0,
      "text": "And if not, can you make yourself smart again?"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 49388.0,
      "end_time": 51154.0,
      "text": "After my neurosurgery,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 51154.0,
      "end_time": 53151.0,
      "text": "part of my brain was missing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 53151.0,
      "end_time": 55924.0,
      "text": "and I had to deal with that."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 55924.0,
      "end_time": 58868.0,
      "text": "It wasn&#39;t the grey matter, but it  was the gooey part dead center"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 58868.0,
      "end_time": 62270.0,
      "text": "that makes key hormones and neurotransmitters."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 62270.0,
      "end_time": 64501.0,
      "text": "Immediately after my surgery,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 64501.00000000001,
      "end_time": 66644.0,
      "text": "I had to decide what amounts of each of over"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 66644.0,
      "end_time": 70346.0,
      "text": "a dozen powerful chemicals to take each day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 70346.0,
      "end_time": 72155.0,
      "text": "because if I just took nothing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 72155.0,
      "end_time": 74887.0,
      "text": "I would die within hours."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 74887.0,
      "end_time": 78807.0,
      "text": "Every day now for 18 years -- every single day --"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 78807.0,
      "end_time": 81517.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve had to try to decide the combinations"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 81517.0,
      "end_time": 82845.0,
      "text": "and mixtures of chemicals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 82845.0,
      "end_time": 86692.0,
      "text": "and try to get them, to stay alive."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 86692.0,
      "end_time": 89413.0,
      "text": "There have been several close calls."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 89413.0,
      "end_time": 93112.0,
      "text": "But luckily, I&#39;m an experimentalist at heart,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 93112.0,
      "end_time": 96339.0,
      "text": "so I decided I would experiment"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 96339.0,
      "end_time": 98779.0,
      "text": "to try to find more optimal dosages"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 98779.0,
      "end_time": 100416.0,
      "text": "because there really isn&#39;t a clear road map"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 100416.0,
      "end_time": 102319.0,
      "text": "on this that&#39;s detailed."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 102319.0,
      "end_time": 104470.0,
      "text": "I began to try different mixtures,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 104470.0,
      "end_time": 107342.0,
      "text": "and I was blown away by how"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 107342.0,
      "end_time": 109753.0,
      "text": "tiny changes in dosages"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 109753.0,
      "end_time": 112902.0,
      "text": "dramatically changed my sense of self,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 112902.0,
      "end_time": 114713.0,
      "text": "my sense of who I was, my thinking,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 114713.0,
      "end_time": 116972.0,
      "text": "my behavior towards people."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 116972.0,
      "end_time": 119210.0,
      "text": "One particularly dramatic case:"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 119210.0,
      "end_time": 120889.0,
      "text": "for a couple months I actually tried dosages"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 120889.0,
      "end_time": 124797.0,
      "text": "and chemicals typical of a man in his early 20s,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 124797.0,
      "end_time": 127808.0,
      "text": "and I was blown away by how my thoughts changed."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 127808.0,
      "end_time": 130928.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 130928.0,
      "end_time": 133986.0,
      "text": "I was angry all the time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 133986.0,
      "end_time": 135832.0,
      "text": "I thought about sex constantly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 135832.0,
      "end_time": 138781.0,
      "text": "and I thought I was the smartest person"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 138781.0,
      "end_time": 140832.0,
      "text": "in the entire world, and"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 140832.0,
      "end_time": 143950.0,
      "text": "—(Laughter)—"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 143950.0,
      "end_time": 146200.0,
      "text": "of course over the years I&#39;d met guys kind of like that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 146200.0,
      "end_time": 148287.0,
      "text": "or maybe kind of toned-down versions of that."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 148287.0,
      "end_time": 150471.0,
      "text": "I was kind of extreme."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 150471.0,
      "end_time": 153400.0,
      "text": "But to me, the surprise was,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 153400.0,
      "end_time": 155206.0,
      "text": "I wasn&#39;t trying to be arrogant."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 155206.0,
      "end_time": 158415.0,
      "text": "I was actually trying,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 158415.0,
      "end_time": 160775.0,
      "text": "with a little bit of insecurity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 160775.0,
      "end_time": 163775.0,
      "text": "to actually fix a problem in front of me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 163775.0,
      "end_time": 165631.0,
      "text": "and it just didn&#39;t come out that way."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 165631.0,
      "end_time": 167114.0,
      "text": "So I couldn&#39;t handle it."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 167114.0,
      "end_time": 168639.0,
      "text": "I changed my dosages."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 168639.0,
      "end_time": 171940.0,
      "text": "But that experience, I think, gave me"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 171940.0,
      "end_time": 172845.0,
      "text": "a new appreciation for men"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 172845.0,
      "end_time": 174661.0,
      "text": "and what they might walk through,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 174661.0,
      "end_time": 176351.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;ve gotten along with men"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 176351.0,
      "end_time": 178190.0,
      "text": "a lot better since then."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 178190.0,
      "end_time": 179734.0,
      "text": "What I was trying to do"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 179735.0,
      "end_time": 181763.0,
      "text": "with tuning these hormones"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 181763.0,
      "end_time": 184860.0,
      "text": "and neurotransmitters and so forth"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 184860.0,
      "end_time": 187691.0,
      "text": "was to try to get my intelligence back"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 187691.0,
      "end_time": 190325.0,
      "text": "after my illness and surgery,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 190325.0,
      "end_time": 192959.0,
      "text": "my creative thought, my idea flow."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 192960.0,
      "end_time": 195601.0,
      "text": "And I think mostly in images,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 195601.0,
      "end_time": 198453.0,
      "text": "and so for me that became a key metric --"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 198453.0,
      "end_time": 200783.0,
      "text": "how to get these mental images"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 200783.0,
      "end_time": 203286.0,
      "text": "that I use as a way of rapid prototyping,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 203287.0,
      "end_time": 205300.0,
      "text": "if you will, my ideas,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 205300.0,
      "end_time": 207402.0,
      "text": "trying on different new ideas for size,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 207402.0,
      "end_time": 209960.0,
      "text": "playing out scenarios."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 209970.0,
      "end_time": 211100.0,
      "text": "This kind of thinking isn&#39;t new."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 211100.0,
      "end_time": 214265.0,
      "text": "Philiosophers like Hume and Descartes and Hobbes"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 214265.0,
      "end_time": 215792.0,
      "text": "saw things similarly."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 215793.0,
      "end_time": 218530.0,
      "text": "They thought that mental images and ideas"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 218530.0,
      "end_time": 220861.0,
      "text": "were actually the same thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 220861.0,
      "end_time": 223278.0,
      "text": "There are those today that dispute that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 223278.0,
      "end_time": 226472.0,
      "text": "and lots of debates about how the mind works,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 226473.0,
      "end_time": 228209.0,
      "text": "but for me it&#39;s simple:"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 228209.0,
      "end_time": 230741.0,
      "text": "Mental images, for most of us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 230741.0,
      "end_time": 234675.0,
      "text": "are central in inventive and creative thinking."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 234675.0,
      "end_time": 236450.0,
      "text": "So after several years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 236450.0,
      "end_time": 239683.0,
      "text": "I tuned myself up and I have lots of great,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 239683.0,
      "end_time": 242731.0,
      "text": "really vivid mental images with a lot of sophistication"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 242731.0,
      "end_time": 245000.0,
      "text": "and the analytical backbone behind them."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 245000.0,
      "end_time": 246921.0,
      "text": "And so now I&#39;m working on,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 246921.0,
      "end_time": 251830.0,
      "text": "how can I get these mental images in my mind"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 251830.0,
      "end_time": 253933.0,
      "text": "out to my computer screen faster?"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 253933.0,
      "end_time": 256220.0,
      "text": "Can you imagine, if you will,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 256220.00000000003,
      "end_time": 258142.00000000003,
      "text": "a movie director being able to use"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 258142.0,
      "end_time": 261904.0,
      "text": "her imagination alone to direct the world in front of her?"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 261904.0,
      "end_time": 265492.0,
      "text": "Or a musician to get the music out of his head?"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 265492.0,
      "end_time": 267784.0,
      "text": "There are incredible possibilities with this"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 267784.0,
      "end_time": 269777.0,
      "text": "as a way for creative people"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 269777.0,
      "end_time": 272100.0,
      "text": "to share at light speed."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 272100.0,
      "end_time": 274800.0,
      "text": "And the truth is, the remaining bottleneck"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 274800.0,
      "end_time": 275181.0,
      "text": "in being able to do this"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 275181.0,
      "end_time": 279161.0,
      "text": "is just upping the resolution of brain scan systems."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 279161.0,
      "end_time": 282190.0,
      "text": "So let me show you why I think  we&#39;re pretty close to getting there"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 282290.0,
      "end_time": 284416.0,
      "text": "by sharing with you two recent experiments"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 284416.0,
      "end_time": 287300.0,
      "text": "from two top neuroscience groups."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 287300.0,
      "end_time": 289491.0,
      "text": "Both used fMRI technology --"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 289491.0,
      "end_time": 291770.0,
      "text": "functional magnetic resonance imaging technology --"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 291770.0,
      "end_time": 293181.0,
      "text": "to image the brain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 293181.0,
      "end_time": 296438.0,
      "text": "and here is a brain scan set from Giorgio Ganis"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 296438.0,
      "end_time": 298388.0,
      "text": "and his colleagues at Harvard."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 298388.0,
      "end_time": 301542.0,
      "text": "And the left-hand column shows a brain scan"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 301542.0,
      "end_time": 304808.0,
      "text": "of a person looking at an image."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 304809.0,
      "end_time": 306738.0,
      "text": "The middle column shows the brainscan"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 306738.0,
      "end_time": 308359.0,
      "text": "of that same individual"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 308359.0,
      "end_time": 311424.0,
      "text": "imagining, seeing that same image."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 311425.0,
      "end_time": 313473.0,
      "text": "And the right column was created"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 313473.0,
      "end_time": 317670.0,
      "text": "by subtracting the middle  column from the left column,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 317830.0,
      "end_time": 320260.0,
      "text": "showing the difference to be nearly zero."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 320260.0,
      "end_time": 322920.0,
      "text": "This was repeated on lots of different individuals"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 322920.0,
      "end_time": 325750.0,
      "text": "with lots of different images,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 325750.0,
      "end_time": 327354.0,
      "text": "always with a similar result."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 327354.0,
      "end_time": 329443.0,
      "text": "The difference between seeing an image"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 329443.0,
      "end_time": 331897.0,
      "text": "and imagining seeing that same image"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 331898.0,
      "end_time": 334530.0,
      "text": "is next to nothing."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 334530.0,
      "end_time": 336814.0,
      "text": "Next let me share with you one other experiment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 336814.0,
      "end_time": 341355.0,
      "text": "this from Jack Gallant&#39;s lab at Cal Berkeley."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 341355.0,
      "end_time": 343418.0,
      "text": "They&#39;ve been able to decode brainwaves"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 343418.0,
      "end_time": 345859.0,
      "text": "into recognizable visual fields."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 345859.0,
      "end_time": 347164.0,
      "text": "So let me set this up for you."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 347164.0,
      "end_time": 349497.0,
      "text": "In this experiment, individuals were shown"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 349497.0,
      "end_time": 351492.0,
      "text": "hundreds of hours of YouTube videos"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 351492.0,
      "end_time": 353531.0,
      "text": "while scans were made of their brains"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 353531.0,
      "end_time": 356747.0,
      "text": "to create a large library of their brain reacting"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 356747.0,
      "end_time": 359396.0,
      "text": "to video sequences."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 359396.0,
      "end_time": 362246.0,
      "text": "Then a new movie was shown with new images,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 362246.0,
      "end_time": 364198.0,
      "text": "new people, new animals in it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 364198.0,
      "end_time": 366909.0,
      "text": "and a new scan set was recorded."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 366909.0,
      "end_time": 369697.0,
      "text": "The computer, using brain scan data alone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 369697.0,
      "end_time": 371721.0,
      "text": "decoded that new brain scan"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 371721.0,
      "end_time": 376970.0,
      "text": "to show what it thought the  individual was actually seeing."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 376970.0,
      "end_time": 379477.0,
      "text": "On the right-hand side, you see the computer&#39;s guess,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 379478.0,
      "end_time": 383485.0,
      "text": "and on the left-hand side, the presented clip."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 383485.0,
      "end_time": 385804.0,
      "text": "This is the jaw-dropper."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 385804.0,
      "end_time": 388491.0,
      "text": "We are so close to being able to do this."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 388491.0,
      "end_time": 391276.0,
      "text": "We just need to up the resolution."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 391276.0,
      "end_time": 394528.0,
      "text": "And now remember that when you see an image"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 394528.0,
      "end_time": 396686.0,
      "text": "versus when you imagine that same image,"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 396686.0,
      "end_time": 400161.0,
      "text": "it creates the same brain scan."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 400161.0,
      "end_time": 402883.0,
      "text": "So this was done with the highest-resolution"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 402883.0,
      "end_time": 405680.0,
      "text": "brain scan systems available today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 405680.0,
      "end_time": 406852.0,
      "text": "and their resolution has increased really"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 406852.0,
      "end_time": 410349.0,
      "text": "about a thousandfold in the last several years."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 410349.0,
      "end_time": 412671.0,
      "text": "Next we need to increase the resolution"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 412671.0,
      "end_time": 414647.0,
      "text": "another thousandfold"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 414648.0,
      "end_time": 416437.0,
      "text": "to get a deeper glimpse."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 416437.0,
      "end_time": 417948.0,
      "text": "How do we do that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 417948.0,
      "end_time": 420561.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s a lot of techniques in this approach."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 420562.0,
      "end_time": 423680.0,
      "text": "One way is to crack open your skull and put in electrodes."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 423680.0,
      "end_time": 425830.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m not for that."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 425830.0,
      "end_time": 428380.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s a lot of new imaging techniques"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 428380.0,
      "end_time": 430410.0,
      "text": "being proposed, some even by me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 430410.0,
      "end_time": 433000.0,
      "text": "but given the recent success of MRI,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 433000.0,
      "end_time": 435680.0,
      "text": "first we need to ask the question,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 435680.0,
      "end_time": 437909.0,
      "text": "is it the end of the road with this technology?"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 437909.0,
      "end_time": 440364.0,
      "text": "Conventional wisdom says the only way"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 440364.0,
      "end_time": 442953.0,
      "text": "to get higher resolution is with bigger magnets,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 442953.0,
      "end_time": 444794.0,
      "text": "but at this point bigger magnets"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 444795.0,
      "end_time": 448545.0,
      "text": "only offer incremental resolution improvements,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 448545.0,
      "end_time": 450705.0,
      "text": "not the thousandfold we need."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 450705.0,
      "end_time": 452527.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m putting forward an idea:"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 452528.0,
      "end_time": 454491.0,
      "text": "instead of bigger magnets,"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 454491.0,
      "end_time": 456941.0,
      "text": "let&#39;s make better magnets."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 456941.0,
      "end_time": 458943.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s some new technology breakthroughs"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 458944.0,
      "end_time": 460401.0,
      "text": "in nanoscience"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 460401.0,
      "end_time": 462128.0,
      "text": "when applied to magnetic structures"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 462128.0,
      "end_time": 465140.0,
      "text": "that have created a whole new class of magnets,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 465141.0,
      "end_time": 467672.0,
      "text": "and with these magnets, we can lay down"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 467672.0,
      "end_time": 469839.0,
      "text": "very fine detailed magnetic field patterns"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 469839.0,
      "end_time": 471194.0,
      "text": "throughout the brain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 471194.0,
      "end_time": 474376.0,
      "text": "and using those, we can actually create"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 474376.0,
      "end_time": 477214.0,
      "text": "holographic-like interference structures"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 477214.0,
      "end_time": 480683.0,
      "text": "to get precision control over many patterns,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 480683.0,
      "end_time": 483128.0,
      "text": "as is shown here by shifting things."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 483128.0,
      "end_time": 486277.0,
      "text": "We can create much more complicated structures"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 486278.0,
      "end_time": 488349.0,
      "text": "with slightly different arrangements,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 488349.0,
      "end_time": 491382.0,
      "text": "kind of like making Spirograph."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 491382.0,
      "end_time": 493610.0,
      "text": "So why does that matter?"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 493610.0,
      "end_time": 496187.0,
      "text": "A lot of effort in MRI over the years"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 496187.0,
      "end_time": 499240.0,
      "text": "has gone into making really big,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 499240.0,
      "end_time": 501634.0,
      "text": "really huge magnets, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 501634.0,
      "end_time": 504143.0,
      "text": "But yet most of the recent advances"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 504143.0,
      "end_time": 506340.0,
      "text": "in resolution have actually come from"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 506340.0,
      "end_time": 510347.0,
      "text": "ingeniously clever encoding and decoding solutions"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 510348.0,
      "end_time": 513635.0,
      "text": "in the F.M. radio frequency transmitters and receivers"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 513635.0,
      "end_time": 516326.0,
      "text": "in the MRI systems."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 516326.0,
      "end_time": 519648.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s also, instead of a uniform magnetic field,"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 519648.0,
      "end_time": 522320.0,
      "text": "put down structured magnetic patterns"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 522320.00000000006,
      "end_time": 525419.0,
      "text": "in addition to the F.M. radio frequencies."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 525419.0,
      "end_time": 527726.0,
      "text": "So by combining the magnetics patterns"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 527726.0,
      "end_time": 530436.0,
      "text": "with the patterns in the F.M. radio frequencies"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 530436.0,
      "end_time": 532607.0,
      "text": "processing which can massively increase"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 532607.0,
      "end_time": 534576.0,
      "text": "the information that we can extract"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 534576.0,
      "end_time": 537220.0,
      "text": "in a single scan."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 537220.0,
      "end_time": 539354.0,
      "text": "And on top of that, we can then layer"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 539354.0,
      "end_time": 543826.0,
      "text": "our ever-growing knowledge  of brain structure and memory"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 543826.0,
      "end_time": 547521.0,
      "text": "to create a thousandfold increase that we need."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 547521.0,
      "end_time": 550464.0,
      "text": "And using fMRI, we should be able to measure"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 550464.0,
      "end_time": 552546.0,
      "text": "not just oxygenated blood flow,"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 552546.0,
      "end_time": 555447.0,
      "text": "but the hormones and neurotransmitters  I&#39;ve talked about"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 555447.0,
      "end_time": 557792.0,
      "text": "and maybe even the direct neural activity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 557792.0,
      "end_time": 559295.0,
      "text": "which is the dream."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 559295.0,
      "end_time": 561529.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re going to be able to dump our ideas"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 561529.0,
      "end_time": 564223.0,
      "text": "directly to digital media."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 564223.0,
      "end_time": 566934.0,
      "text": "Could you imagine if we could leapfrog language"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 566934.0,
      "end_time": 571142.0,
      "text": "and communicate directly with human thought?"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 571143.0,
      "end_time": 574336.0,
      "text": "What would we be capable of then?"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 574336.0,
      "end_time": 576973.0,
      "text": "And how will we learn to deal"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 576973.0,
      "end_time": 581192.0,
      "text": "with the truths of unfiltered human thought?"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 581192.0,
      "end_time": 583759.0,
      "text": "You think the Internet was big."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 583759.0,
      "end_time": 586361.0,
      "text": "These are huge questions."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 586361.0,
      "end_time": 588509.0,
      "text": "It might be irresistible as a tool"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 588509.0,
      "end_time": 592385.0,
      "text": "to amplify our thinking and communication skills."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 592385.0,
      "end_time": 594408.0,
      "text": "And indeed, this very same tool"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 594408.0,
      "end_time": 596534.0,
      "text": "may prove to lead to the cure"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 596534.0,
      "end_time": 599608.0,
      "text": "for Alzheimer&#39;s and similar diseases."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 599608.0,
      "end_time": 603119.0,
      "text": "We have little option but to open this door."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 603120.0,
      "end_time": 604705.0,
      "text": "Regardless, pick a year --"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 604705.0,
      "end_time": 606971.0,
      "text": "will it happen in five years or 15 years?"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 606971.0,
      "end_time": 611587.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s hard to imagine it taking much longer."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 611587.0,
      "end_time": 615282.0,
      "text": "We need to learn how to take this step together."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 615282.0,
      "end_time": 617456.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 617456.0,
      "end_time": 621430.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}